image_analysis.description: A high-resolution photograph of a room or enclosure entirely lined with dark, polished marble. The marble is black or very dark brown with prominent white and gold/tan veining. The image shows a corner where walls meet a tiered seating area or steps, suggesting a steam room, sauna, or high-end bathroom shower. There are bright reflections from overhead lighting on the polished surfaces.
image_analysis.layout: The photograph is taken from a slightly elevated angle looking into a corner. It features vertical wall panels and horizontal surfaces forming steps or benches.

notes: The image appears to be an evidentiary photograph from a legal or investigative production, indicated by the 'EFTA' prefix on the tracking number.
